title: Troye Sivan Debuts 'Talk Me Down' Video, Completing 'Blue Neighborhood' Trilogy
text: Troye Sivan Debuts 'Talk Me Down' Video, Completing 'Blue Neighborhood' Trilogy Saturday, 24 October 2015 (16 minutes ago) Troye Sivan‘s “Blue Neighborhood” trilogy is complete! The 20-year-old social star dropped his new video “Talk Me Down” earlier this week and actually premiered it at Masonic Lodge/Hollywood Forever Cemetery in Los Angeles.
